Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.28,0:39:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不同的波长以不同的角度折射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Different wavelengths are refracted at different angles.{\r}
