Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.29,0:39:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是你看到了彩虹产生了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then you have a rainbow that is produced...{\r}
