Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.54,0:40:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其中的射线要多于其它角度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where there are more rays than at other angles...{\r}
