Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.89,0:40:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是彩虹出现之处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and where the rainbow appears.{\r}
