Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.84,0:40:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是不同于其他人的脑袋影子...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is different than 42 degrees...{\r}
