Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.37,0:40:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就意味着不会有两个人看到完全一模一样的彩虹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This means no two people see the exact same rainbow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.23,0:40:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有时 要是你真够幸运{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Sometimes, if you're really lucky...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.70,0:40:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或至少站在了正确的角度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or at least standing at the right angle...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.93,0:40:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你将会看到副虹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you'll see a secondary rainbow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.38,0:41:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雨滴里所发生的 就是你看到这种衍射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What happens inside the raindrop where you have this diffraction...{\r}
