Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.92,0:41:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此当它第二次跳动时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And so when it bounces a second time...{\r}
