Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.44,0:41:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个更大的角度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's a larger angle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.86,0:41:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}准确说是51度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Fifty-one degrees to be exact.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它会较为暗淡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And it'll be dimmer...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.72,0:41:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为大部分光在第一次跳动后逃逸了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because most of the light escapes after the first bounce...{\r}
