Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.55,0:41:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是其颠倒了排序{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is it's in the opposite order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.73,0:41:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此 一条彩虹一侧的红色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So the red that's on one side on one rainbow...{\r}
