Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.18,0:41:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}彩虹都不会出现在空中的固定点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a rainbow doesn't appear at a fixed point in the sky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.55,0:41:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它的清晰可辨取决于观察者的位置{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Its apparent existence depends solely on the observer's location...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.50,0:41:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以及太阳的方位{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the position of the Sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.31,0:41:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}由此得出 彩虹可视为是一种错觉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In this light, a rainbow may be viewed as an optical illusion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.82,0:41:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}某种程度上说 彩虹是错觉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In some ways, a rainbow is an illusion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.42,0:41:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你无法走进彩虹 接触它 触摸它{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You can't walk to a rainbow and touch it or pick it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.57,0:42:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它始终与你保持着远距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It always maintains its distance away from you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为彩虹其实只是一组光线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}'cause the rainbow really just is a set of light rays...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.33,0:42:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}通过一组角度进入你的眼球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}coming toward your eye from a set of angles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.11,0:42:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要那个方向有水珠{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And as long as there are droplets in those directions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.72,0:42:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就会看到彩虹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you will see a rainbow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.06,0:42:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但要是你前往水珠所在的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But if you go to where the droplets are...{\r}
