Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.45,0:42:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以说确实在那个意义上 彩虹是错觉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So really, in that sense, a rainbow is an illusion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.28,0:42:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}彩虹的简单之美与复杂的科学{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The rainbow's simple beauty and complex science...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.76,0:42:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}使其充满了传奇{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}have imbued it with legend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.53,0:42:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}古希腊人认为{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ancient Greeks considered it a path...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.22,0:42:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它是自己的神祇与凡世之间的通道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}between their gods and the Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.96,0:42:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爱尔兰人的妖精藏金之处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Irish leprechaun's hiding place for his pot of gold...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}据说就在彩虹的尽头{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is said to be at the end of a rainbow...{\r}
