Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.11,0:42:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}印度人相信它是一张弓{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And the Hindus believed it was the bow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.55,0:42:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}属于他们的雷电之神{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}belonging to their god of lightning and thunder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.90,0:43:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}彩虹之美丽{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The beauty of a rainbow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.51,0:43:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光合作用之复杂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the complexity of photosynthesis...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.11,0:43:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}紫外线之影响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the impact of UV rays...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.39,0:43:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}极光之神秘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mystique of an aurora--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.04,0:43:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些形形色色的宇宙现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}these diverse cosmic phenomena...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.51,0:43:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都透露着我们与宇宙之间关系的线索{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}all shed light on our relationship with the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.18,0:43:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们只是被动的旁观者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We are anything but passive bystanders...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.53,0:43:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}冷眼观察天地之间的...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in this whole pageant of phenomena that we see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.46,0:43:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些现象的盛会{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}between Earth and space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.57,0:43:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地球上的生命演化在这种环境中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Life on Earth evolved in this environment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.63,0:43:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有宇宙射线 极光 闪电{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of cosmic rays and aurorae and lightning...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.69,0:43:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们所见到的各种现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and all of the kinds of phenomena that we see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.67,0:43:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是我们得以进化的那种环境的组成部分{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is just part of the environment in which we've evolved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.40,0:43:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以说它和我们难分难解{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And so it is part of us, and we are part of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.62,0:44:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们所见到的美丽的大气现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The beautiful atmospheric phenomena that we see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.26,0:44:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}彩虹 极光 流星飞逝{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}rainbows and auroras and meteors flying by...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.28,0:44:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以及潜在的有害物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as well as the potentially harmful things...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比如来自太阳的紫外线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like UV radiation from the Sun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.36,0:44:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}告诉我们地球并不是什么孤立的星球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}show us the Earth is not just some isolated sphere...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.05,0:44:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}游离于宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}detached from the rest of the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.65,0:44:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 我们是它的一部分{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No, we're part of it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.33,0:44:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这使得世界变得更美好{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This makes the earth more beautiful{\r}
